{"tid":475192,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[武器公投] M16 vs AK47","createTime":"2017-11-21T01:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T14:25:14.000Z","uid":143499,"like":15,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db717a6c92a8000580f9b844b5b7590bb4843943","tid":475192,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:53:50.000Z","msg":"真係叫你當兵打杖，二選一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nM16<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAK47<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上兩把突擊步槍均經歷歲月洗禮，由越戰至今尚未被淘汰，而且是世上最多人認識的突擊步槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nM16: 展開了細口徑(NATO 5.56X45)步槍的熱潮，多年受NATO及西方國家使用，至今依然是美軍常規部隊的武器， 預計將於2018年逐步淘汰<br />\n<br />\nAK47: 以二戰時期德國設計的世上第一把突擊步槍Stg43為設計概念，使用7.62X39 子彈，火力強大卻完全犧牲準繩度， 但由於製作成本極低以及適合於絕大多數嘅環境使用， 所以衍生了不同的版本， 估計於未來30年內依然有大量國家及武裝部隊使用。"},{"pid":"40fd07f30467bb6881c13258b31eddf30877d016","tid":475192,"uid":2720,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"HK416"},{"pid":"29f12d9de6a2e1decfdc32e0c011bf1bda317e47","tid":475192,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HK416</blockquote><br />\n二選一啊！大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講先進我用Honey Badger PDW 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6326676804a8b881c90862d9a4e86bfeab6fc6","tid":475192,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"係M16/AK槍族<br />\n定係原來個兩支？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9d94791e0e28bf410b754648d1141f0fb636d2","tid":475192,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係M16/AK槍族<br />\n定係原來個兩支？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來"},{"pid":"b9b7973eab3d23f4249e97495217c42ccf375ea1","tid":475192,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"M16A4都算，但M4,HK416唔算"},{"pid":"a364d624481dfd1ec130aebea4e6138ff427d2c6","tid":475192,"uid":61589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係M16/AK槍族<br />\n定係原來個兩支？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來</blockquote><br />\nM16都有分M16/A1/A2/A3/A4<br />\nAK47有type I/type II/AKM<br />\n<br />\n你指既原來有無指定邊隻型號定真係最最最original果隻先？"},{"pid":"70891313785cc376f9ba66f7dd7e6484a3124595","tid":475192,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"第一眼睇XM8好撚型仔<br />\n可惜短命"},{"pid":"5824ed55294c0f6082b5fcc11d53e77989a9bc37","tid":475192,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係M16/AK槍族<br />\n定係原來個兩支？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來</blockquote><br />\nM16都有分M16/A1/A2/A3/A4<br />\nAK47有type I/type II/AKM<br />\n<br />\n你指既原來有無指定邊隻型號定真係最最最original果隻先？</blockquote><br />\nall type"},{"pid":"bae66a672aaae8354a39be31fe50565928acff98","tid":475192,"uid":35347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M16A4都算，但M4,HK416唔算</blockquote><br />\n咁AK74算唔算？"},{"pid":"c386e6772b63c9f4a17d9724bd3cc82670517f0d","tid":475192,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M16A4都算，但M4,HK416唔算</blockquote><br />\n點射AK 連射M16<br />\n<br />\n我揀M16"},{"pid":"519bf0099d37fd4349a2b0a0d4552a7c68e0f4d3","tid":475192,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"Google 下 m16 vs ak47<br />\n已經大把資料睇<br />\n<br 