 />\nAK47都有type I/type II/typ III/AKM<br />\n或者犯規d計埋AK103<br />\n咁你又計邊隻先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nonly type I to type III<br />\nAKM 唔算</blockquote><br />\nAKM都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542235f3849e4b6b1268b7b46e256fe8d7cd1f8d","tid":475192,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>M16A4都算，但M4,HK416唔算</blockquote><br />\n咁AK74算唔算？</blockquote><br />\nno<br />\n口徑不一</blockquote><br />\n咁唔洗諗啦<br />\n一條rail都冇點撚用啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由細到大啲friends都話AK47屌打M16<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwait, M16A1都無rail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/120523_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F120523_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=dbf16d83&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔計A4<br />\n點都係M16<br />\n輕同後坐力細<br />\n實際上射速同準繩度都係M16好啲<br />\n同埋M16普通彈都識破片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你要我係博物館攞支槍出嚟打仗就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n代入啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次投二戰SMG"},{"pid":"9ea5b4fcec30f8e845d0797e9deb7b0f8dc22388","tid":475192,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T04:26:06.000Z","msg":"ak<br />\nbtw聽講比m16射中好最易止唔到血死"}]}